ARCHIVE PASSWORD: 2026
================================================================

Core Capabilities
- Dynamic audio driver level interception with sub-millisecond audio frame buffering and delivery synchronization.
- Real-time normalization matrix and automatic volume leveling loops executed on-the-fly.
- Broad digital layout compatibility across common formats including standard PCM (.wav), MP3, FLAC, and OGG formats.
- Smart configuration pattern templates and macro support for automated global hotkey bindings.
- Multi-threaded runtime frameworks designed to maintain high thread priorities and bypass processing line stutter.

